<!-- 'level 2' ritual to purge world corruption -->
:: Gwylan Ritual Select
<<set $outside to 0>><<set $location to "forest_shop">><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set _hideRitualOptions to true>>

You tell Gwylan that you're ready to help enact the ritual.
<br><br>

<<if Time.isBloodMoon() or Time.monthDay is Time.lastDayOfMonth and Time.hour gte 16>>
	<<set _ritualFailSafe to true>><<unset $ritualForced>>
	<<He>> shakes <<his>> head. "Not now. Not on nights like tonight. It's too dangerous."
	<br><br>

	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<elseif Time.hour lte 8>>
	<<set _ritualFailSafe to true>><<unset $ritualForced>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.ritualRequestBlocked to true>>
	<<He>> yawns. "Too early. Breakfast first.<<if $gwylan_cafe_intro>> Meet me at the cafe later?<</if>>"
	<br><br>

	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<else>>

	<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("cautious")>>
		<<if $auriga_scar or $brownFoxRevealed>>
			<<He>> smiles. "You'll forgive me if I'm hesitant to do the more intense ritual. There's much on my mind." <<He>> looks you up and down. "I'm afraid you're bad for my focus right now."
		<<else>>
			<<He>> blinks. "Yes, of course. <span class="purple">We'll be sticking to the less intensive ritual for now.</span> I'm a bit..." <<he>> pauses, shifting to the right slightly and wincing. "Strained."
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<ind>><<link [[Lure a denizen of the forest for purging|Gwylan Forest Journey Prep]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
		<br>
	<<elseif $gwylan.hunting is 3>>
		<<He>> smiles. "Finally. We'll be doing the more advanced ritual. I've missed your touch." <<He>> blushes, and looks away. "I mean, it's more effective, and—" <<he>> stops, taking a deep breath. "<span class="lewd">I've been craving you, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>.</span> It's been too long."
		<br><br>

		<<ind>><<link [[Act as the forest's vessel|Gwylan Ritual Start]]>><</link>><<if $gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_sex")>><<gwylanHypnoNote>><</if>>
		<br>
	<<elseif $gwylan.ritualNext is "sex" or $gwylan.hunting gte 2>>
		<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("heat")>>
			<<He>> moves as if <<hes>> about to leap right over the counter, but stops half way. "Sorry! Sorry. I'm just excited. I need it to just be us this time, though." <<He>> looks away, blushing.
		<<else>>
			<<He>> smiles. "Good, I've been waiting. It'll just be me and you this time." <<He>> winks at you.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<ind>><<link [[Act as the forest's vessel|Gwylan Ritual Start]]>><</link>><<if $gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_sex")>><<gwylanHypnoNote>><</if>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<He>> nods. "We can go out and lure one of the denizens of the forest, or you could act as the forest's vessel yourself. For the latter, <span class="lewd">fluid transfer is mandatory, and there can't be any obstructions</span>."
		<br><br>

		<<ind>><<link [[Lure a denizen of the forest for purging|Gwylan Forest Journey Prep]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
		<br>
		<<ind>><<link [[Act as the forest's vessel|Gwylan Ritual Start]]>><</link>><<if $gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_sex")>><<gwylanHypnoNote>><</if>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<br>

	<<gwylanOptions>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Ritual Start
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set _hideRitualOptions to true>>
You tell Gwylan you want to act as the forest's vessel.
<br><br>

<<if !$settings.tentaclesEnabled or !$settings.hypnosisEnabled>>
	<<set _ritualFailSafe to true>><<unset $ritualForced>>
	<<He>> tilts <<his>> head at you. "Are you sure you're up for this kind of thing?" <<He>> ruffles your hair.
	"It can be an intense process, much more than the other ritual. You might see things you're not prepared for. Things that <span class="lewd">writhe</span> through the holes from the other side may make themselves known.
	You'll also need to be prepared for <span class="lewd">hypnotic influences</span>. <span class="blue">Try opening your mind a bit first, for your own sake.</span>"
	<br><br>

	<i><span class="blue">Tentacles and hypnosis must be enabled to continue.</span></i>
	<br><br>

	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<elseif playerChastity()>>
	<<set $phase to "ritual">>
	<<include "Gwylan Chastity Removal">>
<<else>>
	<<gwylanRitualStart>>
	<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_sex")>>
		<<He>> blushes. "Very well, if you're sure you're ready.
		<<if $wolfpackleader gte 1 or $wolfgirl gte 6 or $fox gte 6 or $dryad gte 6>>
			<span class="green">You're already naturalised to the forest.</span>"
			<<if $wolfgirl gte 6>>
				<<if $transformationParts.wolf.ears isnot "hidden">>
					<<He>> rubs your wolf ears.
				<<else>>
					<<He>> pats your head, right where your wolf ears should be.
				<</if>>
			<<elseif $fox gte 6>>
				<<if $transformationParts.fox.ears isnot "hidden">>
					<<He>> rubs your fox ears.
				<<else>>
					<<He>> pats your head, right where your fox ears should be.
				<</if>>
			<<elseif $dryad gte 6>>
				<<He>> rubs down some of your leaves.
			<<else>>
				<<He>> pats your head. "You're the leader of the local wolf pack, no?" You wonder how <<he>> knows that.
			<</if>>
			"Despite that, there's certain preparations we need to make for the first time.
		<<else>>
			<span class="blue">Since you're not a natural denizen of the forest,</span> there's certain preparations we need to make for the first time.
		<</if>>
		We have to become bonded to one another."
		<br><br>

		<<He>> smiles. "It's a <span class="lewd">mating ritual</span>. A chase in the forest, between you and I. Give me a moment."
		<<He>> vanishes through a dark doorway. You hear the clinking of cookware, and a few minutes later, <<he>> returns with a goblet full of blood-red liquid.
		<br><br>

		/* ToDo: Gwylan - unlock ability to learn wolfbrew (and ghostbrew?) recipe later after this event */
		<<if $wolfpackleader gte 1 or $wolfgirl gte 6 or $fox gte 6 or $dryad gte 6>>
			"This is <span class="purple">wolfbrew</span>. Normally, I'd have to have you drink this, but as said, the forest is already in you. We can start right away.
			<<if $fox gte 6>>
				You could still drink it if you wish, but I wouldn't recommend it. It may dull your foxiness."
			<<elseif $cow gte 6 or $cat gte 6 or $harpy gte 6>>
				You could still drink it if you wish, but you may find it changing your animalistic tendencies to be more... <span class="black">wolfish</span>."
			<<elseif $wolfgirl gte 6>>
				You could still drink it if you wish. It'll make you closer to your inner wolf.
			<<else>>
				You could still drink it if you wish."
			<</if>>
			<<if playerBellyVisible()>>
				<<He>> pauses, before looking down at your <<bellyDescription>>. "It's safe for the child, don't worry."
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			You give it a whiff. It smells like wine.
			<br><br>

			<<link [[Drink|Gwylan Ritual Start Wolfbrew]]>><<tiredness -3>><<drugs 120>><</link>><<ggdrugged>>
			<br>
			<<link [[Do not|Gwylan Ritual Start Hunt]]>><</link>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			"This is <span class="purple">wolfbrew</span>. It'll make you closer to the forest, for a time. You'll need to drink it. It has a kick, so be mindful."
			<<if playerBellyVisible()>>
				<<He>> pauses, before looking down at your <<bellyDescription>>. "It's safe for the child, don't worry."
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			You give it a whiff. It smells like wine.
			<br><br>

			<<link [[Drink|Gwylan Ritual Start Wolfbrew]]>><<tiredness -3>><<drugs 120>><</link>><<ggdrugged>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<He>> smiles. "Very well.
		<<if $wolfpackleader gte 1 or $wolfgirl gte 6 or $fox gte 6 or $dryad gte 6>>
			As you're already part of the forest, we can skip right to the inspection." <<He>> pauses. "We can still repeat the mating ritual if you wish, though."
		<<else>>
			We're already fluid bonded, so we don't need to repeat the mating ritual. Completing it again would make the ritual more effective if you win the chase, though."
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Do the whole ritual|Gwylan Ritual Start Hunt]]>><<tiredness 2>><</link>><<ggtiredness>><<glust>><<gwylanPurgeEffect>>
		<br>
		<<link [[Skip the mating ritual|Gwylan Ritual Start Garden]]>><<endevent>><<set $phase to "skip">><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Ritual Start Wolfbrew
<<effects>>
<<set $sexRitual.wolfbrew to true>>
You bring the goblet to your lips and drink.
<br><br>

It sickly sweet, and burns your throat on the way down. It's intensely invigorating. <span class="pink">A heat rises within you.</span> "You might start growing some extra body hair," Gwylan says. "I probably should have mentioned that."
<br><br>

<<transform wolf 12>>

<<link [[Next|Gwylan Ritual Start Hunt]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Ritual Start Hunt
<<set $outside to 1>><<set $location to "forest">><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<gwylanHuntStart>><<set $huntGame.hunterKnown to true>><<set $sexRitual.chase to true>>
<<set $huntGame.event to "Gwylan Ritual Hunt">>
You're led out to the front of the forest shop.
<br><br>

Gwylan starts stretching. "The rules are simple. If I catch you, I win. If you catch me, you win. If you win, the forest will accept you as one of its own, and the ritual will be more potent. I can't just let you win, though. It has to be a real hunt."
<br><br>

<<if $worn.feet.type.includes("heels")>>
	<<set _linebreak to true>>
	<<He>> glances down at your $worn.feet.name. "Take those off, you'll break an ankle running around the forest with those," <<he>> scolds. <<Hes>> probably right. You stow away your $worn.feet.name and decide to go barefoot.
	<<feetundress "gwylanRitual">>
<</if>>

<<if !_gwylanStatus.includes("wounded") and $brownFoxWoundedTimer>>
	<<unset $brownFoxWoundedTimer>>
	<<He>> cautiously stretches <<his>> right leg. Once it's fully extended, <<he>> smiles. "I've missed running."
	<<if !$brownFoxRevealed>>
		<<He>> pauses. "With a partner, I mean."
	<</if>>
<<elseif _gwylanStatus.includes("wounded")>>
	<<He>> moves <<his>> right leg out, as if testing it. <<He>> briefly winces.
	<<if $brownFoxRevealed>>
		"Unfortunately, my leg hasn't healed yet. I'll push myself, but I'll be slower than normal."
	<<else>>
		"I'm afraid my leg's sprained at the moment, so I'll be slow."
	<</if>>
<</if>>

<<if _gwylanStatus.includesAny("aroused", "lust") and random(0, 2)>>
	<<He>> thinks for a moment, and grins. "I'll be hunting first. You've got twenty seconds. Best start running, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "name">>."
	<br><br>

	You flee into the forest. After a few minutes, you stop to get a feel for the situation.
<<else>>
	<<set $huntGame.hunter to "player">>
	<<He>> thinks for a moment. "You'll be hunting first. Wait twenty seconds, then come get me!" <<He>> doesn't wait for you to respond, and starts running.
	<br><br>

	You wait the requested twenty seconds, and run into the forest after <<him>>. After a few minutes, you stop to get a feel for the situation.
<</if>>
<br><br>

What do you do?
<br>
<<gwylanHuntOptions>>

:: Gwylan Ritual Hunt
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if ($drugged gte 1 or $fox gte 4 or $cat gte 4 or $wolfgirl gte 4) and !random(0, 10) and $huntGame.turn gte 1>>
	The forest is in you.
<<else>>
	You are in the forest.
<</if>>
<<gwylanHuntEffects>>

<<if $huntGame.end>>
	<<tiredness 1>>
	<br><br>
	<<if $huntGame.end is "ambushSuccess">>
		<<if $huntGame.otherHealth lte 1>>
			With a final, determined pounce, you <span class="green">catch <<= $huntGame.adversaryText>></span>. <<He>> squirms under you, but you hold <<his>> wrists down to the ground firmly. <<He>> submits. <<npcincr Gwylan lust 3>><<gglust>>
		<<elseif $huntGame.otherHealth is 2>>
			With a predatory pounce, you tackle <<= $huntGame.adversaryText>>. You roll with <<him>> for a moment, but <<he>> manages to squirm away. <span class="teal">You know <<he>> won't be able to escape again.</span>

			<<if !$huntGame.brownFox and $awarelevel gte 4 and _gwylanTF.known and $huntGame.otherHealth lte 2 and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4 and !_gwylanStatus.includes("wounded")>>
				<<set $huntGame.brownFox to true>><<set $huntGame.adversaryText to "the brown fox">>
				<<set $huntGame.skills.athleticsMax += 75>><<set $huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMax += 75>><<set $huntGame.skills.danceMax += 75>>
				<br><br>

				You stand up. You don't see Gwylan running away from you. You see something else.
				<br><br>

				<span class="red">It's a massive brown fox. The air around it blurs as it runs away from you on all fours.</span>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			You pounce like a well-trained predator, and get your hands on <<= $huntGame.adversaryText>>. <<Hes>> fast, though. After a brief struggle, <<he>> manages to slip away from you.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<if $huntGame.otherHealth lte 1>>
			<<set $sexRitual.chaseWon to true>><<set $sexRitual.purge++>>
			<span class="gold">You've won the hunt!</span> <<gwylanPurgeEffect>>
			<br><br>

			<<if $huntGame.brownFox>>
				Your head suddenly feels more clear. You look down and see Gwylan beneath you rather than the fox. <<His>> face is bright red.
			<<else>>
				Gwylan looks up at you, <<his>> face bright red.
			<</if>>
			/* ToDo: Gwylan - variation for when Gwylan is in heat and gets caught or catches the player */
			"Alright, you can get off of me now. You win." <<He>> smiles.
			<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("wounded")>>
				"You're lucky I'm hobbled. It wouldn't have been so easy otherwise." <<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><<gyearning>>
			<<else>>
				"That was incredible! You moved so quickly." <<npcincr Gwylan dom 3>><<ggyearning>>
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			You help Gwylan stand. The two of you walk back to the shop. <<tiredness 6>><<ggtiredness>>
			<br><br>

			<<link [[Next|Gwylan Ritual Start Garden]]>><<endevent>><<unset $huntGame>><<pass 10>><</link>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<set $huntGame.otherHealth-->>
			<<gwylanHuntOptions>>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $huntGame.end is "ambushFailed">>
		<<if $huntGame.hunter is "player">>
			You miss your pounce, and <<he>> starts to run!
			<br><br>

			<<if $huntGame.otherHealth lte 1>>
				This is the final stretch. <span class="green">If you catch <<him>> now, it's over.</span>
				<br><br>
			<</if>>

			<<link [[Chase!|Gwylan Ritual Chase]]>><<set $chasestart to 1>><</link>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			You miss your pounce, and <<he>> makes a grab for you!
			<br><br>

			<<link [[Run!|Gwylan Ritual Chase]]>><<set $runstart to 1>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $huntGame.end is "chase">>
		<<if $huntGame.otherHealth lte 1>>
			This is the final stretch. <span class="green">If you catch <<him>> now, it's over.</span>
			<br><br>
		<</if>>

		<<link [[Chase!|Gwylan Ritual Chase]]>><<set $chasestart to 1>><</link>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<if !$huntGame.brownFox and $awarelevel gte 4 and _gwylanTF.known and $huntGame.otherHealth lte 2 and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4 and !_gwylanStatus.includes("wounded")>>
			<<set $huntGame.brownFox to true>><<set $huntGame.adversaryText to "the brown fox">>
			<<set $huntGame.skills.athleticsMax += 75>><<set $huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMax += 75>><<set $huntGame.skills.danceMax += 75>>
			Except this isn't Gwylan.
			<br><br>

			<span class="red">It's a massive brown fox, its three eyes glowing a bright green. The air around it blurs as it pounces at you.</span>
			<br><br>
		<</if>>

		<<if $phase isnot "noDodge" and !$huntGame.noDodge>>
			<<link [[Dodge!|Gwylan Ritual Chase Dodge]]>><</link>><<dancedifficulty $huntGame.skills.danceMin $huntGame.skills.danceMax>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<link [[Run!|Gwylan Ritual Chase]]>><<set $runstart to 1>><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<set $huntGame.tracked to false>>
	<<set $huntGame.distance to 2>>
	<<set $huntGame.playerAction to "">>
	<<set $huntGame.playerActionLast to "">>
	<<set $huntGame.playerTracked to false>><<set $huntGame.playerTrackedKnown to false>>
	<<run delete $huntGame.noMoreHiding>><<run delete $huntGame.otherHideTimer>>
	<<set $huntGame.otherAction to "run">>
	<<set $huntGame.turn to 0>>
	<<set $huntGame.end to false>>
<<else>>
	<<gwylanHuntState>>
	<<gwylanHuntOptions>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Ritual Chase Dodge
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $huntGame.dance ||= 0>>
<<if $danceSuccess>>
	<<set $huntGame.skills.danceMin += 100>><<set $huntGame.skills.danceMax += 175>>
	<<if $huntGame.dance is 0>>
		You <<dancetext>> grab <<him>> mid-pounce. You spin with <<his>> momentum in a dance-like twirl before pushing <<him>> away. <<He>> lands, and pounces again!
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Dodge again!|Gwylan Ritual Chase Dodge]]>><</link>><<dancedifficulty $huntGame.skills.danceMin $huntGame.skills.danceMax>>
		<br>
		<<link [[Run!|Gwylan Ritual Chase]]>><<set $huntGame.dance to 0>><<set $runstart to 1>><</link>>
		<br>
	<<elseif $huntGame.dance is 1>>
		<<if $huntGame.brownFox>>
			As <<he>> pounces, you expect to catch <<him>> by <<his>> front legs. Instead, your hands meet soft skin. Gwylan's determined face meets you instead of the fox's.
		<</if>>
		You <<dancetext>> grab <<him>> by the wrists and twirl <<him>> around you. Your dance continues, and you think you see the faintest hint of a smile from Gwylan.
		<br><br>

		<span class="blue">If you run now, you'll have a good head start on <<him>>.</span> Once more, <<he>> pounces for you!
		<br><br>

		<<if $huntGame.otherHealth lte 1>>
			<<link [[Dance|Gwylan Ritual Chase Dodge]]>><</link>><<dancedifficulty $huntGame.skills.danceMin $huntGame.skills.danceMax>>
		<<else>>
			<span class="blue">If you wear <<him>> down more, it might be possible to counter-attack next time.</span>
		<</if>>
		<br>
		<<link [[Run!|Gwylan Ritual Chase]]>><<set $huntGame.chaseDistance to 3>><<set $huntGame.dance to 0>><<set $runstart to 1>><</link>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		One final time, you <<dancetext>> sidestep, grab, and twirl.
		<br><br>

		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning") and ($hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4 or $auriga_scar or C.npc.Gwylan.dom gte 140)>>
			For a moment, this isn't a hunt anymore. The forest itself yields to your grace. Gwylan does, too. Time slows down.
			<br><br>

			You don't try to throw <<him>> aside this time, nor does <<he>> try to topple you over. Instead, you lean into each other.
			<br><br>

			You embrace.
			<br><br>

			You dance.
			<br><br>

			You step in time with six <span class="teal">familiar</span> notes. A pause. The first note staggers before the next bar, and its five siblings catch up. You repeat it three times.
			<br><br>

			You're no longer where you once were.
			<br><br>

			<<link [[Next|Gwylan Ritual Chase Dance]]>><</link>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			You have <<him>>, and you're not letting go this time. You push forward, letting your momentum do the rest of the work, and pin <<= $huntGame.adversaryText>> to the ground.
			<<He>> squirms under you, but you hold <<his>> wrists down to the ground firmly. <<He>> submits. <<npcincr Gwylan lust 3>><<gglust>>
			<br><br>

			<<set $sexRitual.chaseWon to true>>
			<span class="gold">You've won the hunt!</span>
			<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning")>>
				<span class="blue">Yet, your graceful dance leaves you feeling as though you were on the cusp of something more, were your <<if V.worn.neck.name === "familiar collar" && V.worn.neck.cursed === 1>>Devotion<<else>>Curiosity<</if>> deeper.</span>
			<</if>>
			<<set $sexRitual.purge++>><<gwylanPurgeEffect>>
			<br><br>

			<<if $huntGame.brownFox>>
				Your head suddenly feels more clear. You look down and see Gwylan beneath you rather than the fox. <<His>> face is bright red.
			<<else>>
				Gwylan looks up at you, <<his>> face bright red.
			<</if>>
			"Alright, you can get off of me now. You win." <<He>> smiles.
			<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("wounded")>>
				"Even with my leg hurt, you moved with me gracefully. I'll be feeling it tomorrow, but it was worth it." <<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><<gyearning>>
			<<else>>
				"That was amazing. You moved so... gracefully." <<npcincr Gwylan dom 3>><<ggyearning>>
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			You help Gwylan stand. The two of you walk back to the shop. <<tiredness 6>><<ggtiredness>>
			<br><br>

			<<link [[Next|Gwylan Ritual Start Garden]]>><<endcombat>><<clotheson>><<unset $huntGame>><<pass 10>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<set $huntGame.dance++>>
<<else>>
	<<if $huntGame.playerHealth is 3>>
		You try to dodge, <span class="red">but you're too slow</span>. Or, rather, <<hes>> too fast.
		<br><br>

		<<if $huntGame.brownFox>>
			<<His>> claws nearly take you, but instead only snag. You fall to the ground as <<he>> darts by. <<pain 2>><<gpain>>
			<br><br>
		<<else>>
			<<He>> grabs you, and you fall. <<He>> does too, a short distance away.
		<</if>>
		You have enough time to get back on your feet, but <<he>> quickly pounces again.
		<br><br>

		<<if $huntGame.dance gte 2>>
			<<if $huntGame.otherHealth lte 1>>
				<<link [[Dance|Gwylan Ritual Chase Dodge]]>><</link>><<dancedifficulty $huntGame.skills.danceMin $huntGame.skills.danceMax>>
			<<else>>
				<span class="blue">If you wear <<him>> down more, it might be possible to counter-attack.</span>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[Dodge again!|Gwylan Ritual Chase Dodge]]>><</link>><<dancedifficulty $huntGame.skills.danceMin $huntGame.skills.danceMax>>
		<</if>>
		<br>
		<<link [[Run!|Gwylan Ritual Chase]]>><<set $huntGame.dance to 0>><<set $runstart to 1>><</link>>
		<br>
	<<elseif $huntGame.playerHealth is 2>>
		Once again, you try to dodge, <span class="red">but <<hes>> too fast</span>.
		<br><br>

		<<if $huntGame.brownFox>>
