:: Gwylan Ritual Chase Dance
<<set $location to "estate">><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
You're not sure where you are.
<br><br>

You're not sure that you care.
<br><br>

<<if $fox gte 6 and ($demon gte 6 or $auriga_scar)>>
	<<set _masked to "antlered fox">>
<<elseif $fox gte 6 or isLoveInterest("Avery")>>
	<<set _masked to "fox">>
<<elseif $demon gte 6>>
	<<set _masked to "elk">>
<<elseif $wolfgirl gte 6>>
	<<set _masked to "hound">>
<<else>>
	<<set _masked to "rat">>
<</if>>

The world around you is dim, obscured by the eyesockets of the <<= _masked>> mask on your face.
<br><br>

Gwylan dances with you, wearing
<<if _masked is "antlered fox">>
	a fox mask of <<his>> own, although <<his>> antlers have been broken off.
<<elseif _masked is "fox">>
	a fox mask of <<his>> own.
<<else>>
	a fox mask.
<</if>>
<<His>> tunic is gone, replaced by
<<if C.npc.Gwylan.pronoun is "m">>
	a frilly suit, decorated with white roses.
<<else>>
	a frilly dress, decorated with red roses.
<</if>>
<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
	There's a wrapping around the back, allowing <<his>> tail to stick out. It wags back and forth gently as you dance.
<</if>>
<br><br>

Others dance around you.
<<if _masked is "elk">>
	The other elks watch with leering envy.
<<else>>
	Leery elk masks watch with envy.
<</if>>
Their arms grab for you, but never reach. Their gazes strip you both bare, but neither of you pay it any mind. They don't matter. They have no power over you right now.
<br><br>

Gwylan leans into you as the dance slows. This close, you notice <<if _masked is "antlered fox">>another<<else>>a<</if>> flaw in <<his>> mask. There's a cracked mark perfectly centered on the forehead. It bleeds. <<He>> either doesn't notice or doesn't care.
<br><br>

There is nothing in the forest but the two of you. You are in the forest, and the forest is in you.
<br><br>

You are One.
<br><br>

Gwylan
<<switch $bodysize>>
	<<case 0 1>>tilts your head up,
	<<case 2>>leans in,
	<<case 3>>stands on the tips of <<his>> toes,
<</switch>>
and kisses you. <<takeKissVirginity "Gwylan" "romantic">>
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Gwylan Ritual Chase Dance 2]]>><<if $arousal lt 6000>><<set $arousal to 6000>><</if>><</link>>
<br>

